.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-NOTES-TAG-SUMMARY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-notes-tag-summary \- FEAT-2113 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-notes-tag-summary
.SH DESCRIPTION
Report tag counts from the wallet notes database, grouped by tag (FEAT-2113).
Gracefully handles a missing or inaccessible wallet DB.
.PP
Output: JSON.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
